                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002002,
            "text": "to the end that ye be not quickly shaken from your mind, nor yet be troubled, either by spirit, or by word, or by epistle as from us, as that the day of the Lord is just at hand; ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-2",
            "footnotes": [],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002003,
            "text": "let no man beguile you in any wise: for , except the falling away come first, and the man of <i>[c]</i>sin be revealed, the son of perdition, ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-3",
            "footnotes": [
                {
                    "c": "Many ancient authorities read <i>lawlessness</i>."
                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002004,
            "text": "he that opposeth and exalteth himself against all that is called God or <i>[d]</i>that is worshipped; so that he sitteth in the <i>[e]</i>temple of God, setting himself forth as God. ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-4",
            "footnotes": [
                {
                    "d": "Greek <i>an object of worship</i>. [[Acts 17:23]]."
                },
                {
                    "e": "Or, <i>sanctuary</i>"
                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002005,
            "text": "Remember ye not, that, when I was yet with you, I told you these things? ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-5",
            "footnotes": [],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002006,
            "text": "And now ye know that which restraineth, to the end that he may be revealed in his own season. ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-6",
            "footnotes": [],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002007,
            "text": "For the mystery of lawlessness doth already work: <i>[f]</i>only  one that restraineth now, until he be taken out of the way. ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-7",
            "footnotes": [
                {
                    "f": "Or, <i>only until he that now restraineth be taken etc.</i>"
                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002008,
            "text": "And then shall be revealed the lawless one, whom the Lord <i>[g]</i>Jesus shall <i>[h]</i>slay with the breath of his mouth, and bring to nought by the manifestation of his <i>[i]</i>coming; ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-8",
            "footnotes": [
                {
                    "g": "Some ancient authorities omit <i>Jesus</i>."
                },
                {
                    "h": "Some ancient authorities read <i>consume</i>."
                },
                {
                    "i": "Greek <i>presence</i>."
                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002009,
            "text": ", whose <i>[j]</i>coming is according to the working of Satan with all <i>[k]</i>power and signs and lying wonders, ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-9",
            "footnotes": [
                {
                    "j": "Greek <i>presence</i>."
                },
                {
                    "k": "Greek <i>power and signs and wonders of falsehood</i>."
                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002010,
            "text": "and with all deceit of unrighteousness for them that <i>[l]</i>perish; because they received not the love of the truth, that they might be saved. ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-10",
            "footnotes": [
                {
                    "l": "Or, <i>are perishing</i>"
                }
            ],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002011,
            "text": "And for this cause God sendeth them a working of error, that they should believe a lie: ",
            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-11",
            "footnotes": [],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
