            "version": "ASV",
            "clsstr": "2Thess-2-12",
            "footnotes": [],
            "crossrefs": []
        },
        {
            "verse_id": 53002013,
            "text": "\u00b6 But we are bound to give thanks to God always for you, brethren beloved of the Lord, for that God chose you <i>[m]</i>from the beginning unto salvation in sanctification of the Spirit and <i>[n]</i>belief of the truth: ",
